mona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-22\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-06-24\" who=\"#AL\">Andoni Llamazares added a new text edition\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2023-01-04\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag added bibliography and amended metadata\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001312_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001312.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#AL\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"idionym\">Λουκίφερα\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>ζῶσα ἑαυ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>τῇ ἐποίησεν\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>καὶ τοῖς ἰδίοις\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>πᾶσιν\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>text according to IG\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The formula is a distinctively Latin one. Ferrua suggests the text is of Christian date (on the basis that Amico attributed it to a christian cemetery; but the necropolis outside Porta Stesicora covers a much wider period than this), but Korhonen reasonably suggests that it need not be so.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Kaibel\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1890\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">489\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Franz\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1853\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>5715\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/TQMVHEVL\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>247-248 n.38\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/NMS48IZF\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001897\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001897\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n\t       \u003Cbibl>\n\t           \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n\t           \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n\t           \u003CcitedRange>114 no.432\u003C/citedRange>\n\t           \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/759ZXHKQ\"/>\n\t       \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n\t   \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
